{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"1195-inyanga-nekepisi","title":"Inyanga nekepisi","description":"Umfanyana othile uphiwa ikepisi eluhlaza ngumama wakhe. Suke umoya uyivuthuze ikepisi iyowela esihlahleni. Ebusuku kuvele omunye umuntu egqoke le kepisi. Ingabe uzobuye ayithole ikepisi yakhe?","language":"isiZulu","langCode":"zu","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Zimbili  Dlamini"],"illustrators":["Angie & Upesh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/1195-inyanga-nekepisi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700911/size3/a7997747b4c2afe36ad258eb24979534.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700911/size6/a7997747b4c2afe36ad258eb24979534.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2789/size6/aaabacbf8e365331cc12d5c6d1166426.jpg","text":"Sonke sahamba saya endalini yasemakethe .","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2790/size6/cc128b0eba6ee81ca35645633730dc40.jpg","text":"Ubaba wathengela uXolani izibuko ezinhle.\nUmama wangithengela ikepisi egqamile eluhlaza sasibhakabhaka.\nIngane yona yathola uswidi.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2791/size6/71d6d252238a3ceb3948291ba2865fad.jpg","text":"Endleleni eya ekhaya kwaba nesivunguvungu somoya.\nSaphephula ikepisi lami.\n4/12","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2792/size6/08a18c29e1aff75deb9416131409b928.jpg","text":"Ikepisi lami lagaxela esihlahleni.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2793/size6/cbb7590914f9a56a1e420873d491a8cf.jpg","text":"Ngakhala kakhulu angizange ngidle nesidlo sami sakusihlwa.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2794/size6/30c5a5325f67da008f08afe0d26b3d15.jpg","text":"Ngabo lobobusuku, kwaphuma inyanga yakhanyisa ngqoekepisini lami elisesihlahleni.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2795/size6/698b1c39dee9c67c31d1eb2bbc86a603.jpg","text":"Inyanga yayilinganisa ikepisi lami yase imamatheka, nami ngahleka.\n8/12","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2796/size6/a923f4c88afca7f7f21bd661a5f57f63.jpg","text":"Ngosuku olulandelayo ukuphuma kwesikole umama wanginika ikepisi entsha ebomvu.\n“Ilethwe yinyanga,” kusho umama.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2797/size6/70673625fc413701734cc82521eb0ce9.jpg","text":"Ngalobobusuku mina nenyanga sawagqoka amakepisi ethu sahleka.\nSasijabule.\n10/12","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2798/size6/43a09a01293fed4b7626ce466ed01489.jpg","text":"Ucabanga ukuthi ilanga iyasidinga isigqoko?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2799/size6/7db264d4d80d4c90b80894f15d14e1da.jpg","text":"Qagela yisiphi isigqoko engisigqoke namuhla!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":91}}